---
title: Lemony Salmon & Cacio e Pepe Linguine with Crispy Broccoli, Burst Tomatoes, and Chilies
description: Cacio e Pepe means salt and pepper in Italian, and usually refers to a simple pasta dish consisting of just Parmesan, salt, and freshly cracked black pepper. We’re adding tender broccoli, burst tomatoes, and a few other twists to the mix for an unbeatable pasta dinner.
